adjectives.description: paganish (comparative more paganish, superlative most paganish)

examples: Nor can he be so little acquainted with the paganish theology, as not to apprehend a vast disagreement between this and that, and a much greater agreement between the paganish notion of the Deity, and his own.
Actually Godsmack has a lot of paganish songs because the lead singer Sully is Wiccan.
